  <p>
    When you visit Hireables, our web server sends a cookie to your device, which allows us to recognize your device (but not the person using it). By associating the identification secret stored in the cookies with other account information stored in our database when, for example, you log into the Services, we know that the cookie information relates to your hungryhead account.
  </p>

