    <h3>Security</h3>
    <p>
      Cookies help us protect your account from being accessed by anyone other than you, alert you and us when your account is accessed, and provide capabilities that allow us to disable any active sessions you have (for example, when you log out or change your password).
    </p>

    <h3>Saving preferences</h3>
    <p>
      Hireables uses cookies that provide functionality and help us deliver our products and services better — for example, by storing your preferences, which help us tailor our views accordingly.
    </p>

    <h3>Analytics and research</h3>
    <p>
      Cookies and other analytical technologies help us learn, improve, and research features and content on the Hireables website. For example, we may use cookies to determine which types of browsers or devices you are using to access Hireables or which areas of our website you are least interested in so that we can make your experience more meaningful.
