<div>
  <h3>Opting out</h3>
  <p>
    We truly respect your privacy and therefore, we do not collect or share any of your personal information. Most of the information we collect is essential for our service to function smoothly across all devices and OS platforms.
  </p>
  <p>
    Most web browsers are built around cookies and automatically accept cookies but, if you prefer, you can change your browser settings to prevent that or to notify you each time a cookie is set. You can also learn more about cookies by visiting www.allaboutcookies.org, which includes essential information on cookies and how to block cookies using different browsers. Please note that blocking or deleting cookies may prevent you from using full features of our Services.
